msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Hm? It feels like someone's watching me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "I must be imagining it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "No time for questions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "What the hell just happened to me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Hey. Y'look like y'just saw a ghost."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Y'did see it, didn't ya? Carryin' a sword."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah. I actually did more than just see it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Well, I'm the gravekeeper 'round these parts.\r\nStopped by 'cause somethin' felt off tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Guess that was yer fault."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Wait. You've seen the ghost here, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Y'ain't from here, are ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Local folks wouldn't dare swing 'round my graveyard.\r\nEven kids're afraid t'come anywhere near."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I ain't even heard of an outsider who\r\nwas brave enough t'show his face in here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Huh. I had no idea."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Don't worry 'bout it.\r\nI ain't tryin' to bring ya down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "If the legends're true, the ghosts that show up 'round\r\nhere are pirates who raided the Inland Sea ages ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "(Pirates...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "These guys're a real rowdy bunch.\r\nEven in death, they're always itchin' fer a fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "If yer feelin' up to it, y'should come\r\nback and humor 'em sometime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Pirate ghosts, huh?\r\nEven in a quiet town like this, I can't catch a break."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Something feels off again.\r\nIt must be the pirate ghosts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Long time no see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "What? There are two of you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Ugh, that's enough sleeping on the ground for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "I knew ya'd be back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "What's yer name, kid?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu. Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, huh? Our spectral buddies're\r\nreally warmin' up to ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "And how exactly do you know that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "I've been watchin' over this place fer years.\r\nI can tell how they feel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Y'probly can't feel it, but there's a real lively\r\nenergy flowin' through the air right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Well it's usually real gloomy 'round here,\r\nbut it feels like the ghosts're takin' a shine t'ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Bet they're jus' lovin' all these fights."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "This doesn't make much sense."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Y'know what? Y'might jus' be the one\r\nt'finally put their souls t'rest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "The ghosts are here. I can feel it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "I'm not that interested in fighting you guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "But I've done this much. I'll keep\r\ngoing until your souls are at peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Let's do this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Ugh, I wish I didn't pass out every time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Hm? It doesn't look like\r\nthe gravekeeper's coming this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "They should be here soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "So you're still trying to up the ante.\r\nThink three of you is enough to stop me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "You guys are quick, but I promise you won't be\r\ngetting the jump on me any time soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Every time it's the same thing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "So yer back in style, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Thanks t'ya, the fog that's been hangin' over\r\nthis graveyard's finally startin' t'clear up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "I reckon it's 'cause yer resolvin' the regrets\r\nthose ghosts have about their ol' lives."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Who exactly are you, old man?\r\nAre you some kind of psychic?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Well, I'm roughly a tenth-generation\r\ndescendant of the ghosts y'been fightin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "You're related to them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Y'remember how I said they used t'be pirates\r\nback when they were still alive?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "T'be more precise, they were actually mercenaries\r\nwho were hired by a big band o' pirates."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "Go on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Back 'round Nobunaga's time, in the 1500s, the pirates\r\no' Hiroshima got in a real big war with each other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "In order t'tip the scales in their favor, one group\r\no' pirates hired these three legendary mercenaries."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Story goes those three coulda taken over the whole\r\ncountry with jus' a sword if they were feelin' up to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Turns out they didn't really have sea legs, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Got so sick they couldn't even draw their swords.\r\nThey actually ended up fallin' overboard n' drownin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "All three of them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Mhm. All at the same time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "That's absurd."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "'Cause their prized mercenaries were gone, the pirates\r\nwho hired 'em got obliterated by a rival crew."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "So, the three of 'em died without fully honin'\r\ntheir skills. 'At's what they're regrettin' now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "And that's why they're so eager to fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "As their descendant, I've been hopin' fer a while now\r\nthat somebody'd come along n' lay 'em down fer good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "'Til that happens, they're jus' gonna\r\nkeep wanderin' around this graveyard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "I gotta say, though... I'm thinkin' y'might be\r\nthe one who can finally put 'em to rest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Yer probly the only person in the world who's\r\ngot the raw manpower y'need to do it. So..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Jus' one more fight. A final flourish t'let their\r\nsouls drift into the ether in peace. Please, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Our last battle, huh?\r\nIt'll be sad to say goodbye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "It seems like this will be the last time\r\nI deal with these graveyard ghosts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Right, then. They really are ready to end this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Hey, can I ask a favor of you guys?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I always wake up on the ground after our fights,\r\nso my clothes get covered in dirt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "I was hoping you could help me with that somehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "I wonder if they heard me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "This is... my apartment?\r\nHow did I get here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "And what ended up happening to the ghosts?\r\nI should head over to the graveyard..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Allow me t'thank ya. 'Cause of ya,\r\nmy ancestors can finally rest in peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "How can you tell, old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Trust me, I have my ways."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "I've really gotta thank ya fer this. Y'did\r\nwhat none o' their descendants could ever manage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I enjoyed going up against them, too.\r\nIt turned into some pretty decent sparring practice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Interestin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Y'know, I've always regretted not bein' able t'help\r\nmy ancestors. Guess ya helped ease my regrets, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah. I'd be honored if ya'd accept this,\r\nKiryu-san. It's the only way I got t'thank ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "What is this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "It's a talisman t'ward off spirits n' the like.\r\nY'won't see any more ghosts so long as yer holdin' it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "That's almost depressing to hear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Does that mean..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Hold on, just what was all of that...?"
msgstr ""

